extends index
block content 

  h3 Howdy!
  h5 It's me, your over-protective big sister.
  p Whether you're going on a run or walking home at night, give me a heads up. I won't judge you. I won't tell your mom unless you tell me to.
  ul.collection
    li.collection-item I'll ask you where you're going and what time you'll be back.
    li.collection-item I'll start a timer and count down till your return time.
    li.collection-item When you get home, enter your four-digit passcode. I won't text anyone!
    li.collection-item If you don't make it home by your return time, I'll text your emergency contacts and let them know.
    li.collection-item If you enter your emergency code while you're out, I'll text your emergency contacts and tell them that you might be in trouble.

  a(href="/trip/start")
    button.btn() I'm Going Out!